{"tid":1463784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[文長]有個金管局員工有野想同大家講有關816行動","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T00:28:25.000Z","uid":67149,"like":225,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"5826c6de0d83f7614b52f9ce846e18047cefe555","tid":1463784,"uid":67149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:46:30.000Z","msg":"個員工就係我啦<br />\n作為一個金管局員工，<br />\n又見816撳錢+換外幣行動好似無咩回響，<br />\n我就喺度分析下呢單野嘅可行性，<br />\n同埋可以利用佢黎做啲乜。<br />\n<br />\n背景: 我諗個個都知，一個國家/地方有個穩定既貨幣對佢既經濟好重要，<br />\n而對香港呢個外向型嘅經濟體系，<br />\n一個極度倚賴貿易同融資活動嘅地方，港幣一收皮基本上成個香港都可以收得皮。<br />\n<br />\n咁點先可以令到港幣收皮？<br />\n個人認為係好難，<br />\n因為你要打爆港幣，<br />\n你先要破壞到個聯繫匯率，<br />\n姐係要破壞40000億港幣嘅外匯基金，<br />\n齋靠普通市民撳錢同沽港幣基本上都無乜可能沽得爆40000億。<br />\n<br />\n但係   我地絕對可以靠㩒錢呢樣野去製造一個 <br />\n<strong>港紙就快變廢紙 嘅白色恐怖。</strong><br />\n今日EOB港幣最新quote價係7.8458，<br />\n距離聯繫匯率弱方兌換保證7.85<strong>非常接近</strong>，<br />\n當港幣一跌到7.85，<br />\n金管局就有責任動用外匯基金裡面嘅美元資產去接哂所有7.85嘅沽盤。<br />\n假如816我地成功號召到幾千人去㩒錢，<br />\n沽到港幣掂到7.85就可以逼到金管局出手。<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少「港幣回弱觸弱方兌換保證」既破壞力，<br />\n呢個係港幣變弱嘅一個大指標，<br />\n而實際上有好多人（特別係果d收埋唔知幾多棺材錢喺銀行嘅廢老）都無留意嘅係，<br />\n2018年開始其實港幣已經掂過幾次7.85，<br />\n金管局喺呢年幾入面購入合共超過2000億港幣，<br />\n用年幾時間去KO左滾存左差唔多成100年歷史<br />\n外匯基金嘅5%。<br />\n<br />\n雖然要沽爆港幣係唔容易，<br />\n但用㩒錢黎做個火引去破壞銀行甚至去影響外匯基金嘅運作係絕對可行，我嘅建議係咁:<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>㩒錢限期要快同狠</strong></span>，816-818呢個週末係好時機，<br />\n一來星期五六日多啲人得閒，二來銀行放假，<br />\n佢地就算要變賣手頭上資產去換錢都要起碼等到星期一(再加T+2 settlement)先做到。<br />\n一間銀行每日都有無數衍生工具同各種數嘅settlement要做，<br />\n當佢liquidity出現問題，一單數找唔到，就有機會有骨牌效應嘅出現。<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> Focus某一兩間銀行，個人建議中銀，</span></strong><br />\n一來佢阿媽要幫習狗打貿易戰，唔會承擔到太多風險，<br />\n二來佢普及性高，好多人都有佢户口，仲係jetco銀行，周街都係atm比人撳。<br />\n3. 816係個火引，真正可以引爆嘅係果d收埋大把錢喺銀行嘅廢老，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">所以文宣一定要足。</span></span></strong><br />\n建議集中多d喺已發生嘅事實度(例如上面所講金管局用年幾時間去回購左2000幾億）。<br />\n4. 㩒錢嘅效果一定好過唱外匯，因為銀行最怕唔係無港幣，係無錢姐。<br />\n唔夠港幣隨時都仲可以同發鈔行換，但無錢就真係乜流動性資產都無哂。<br />\n<br />\n所以...<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">816 一齊撳錢</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5abda7d46d793332181f4d8e2e6e3efe2ece9d6","tid":1463784,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"推, 諗左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e90e8bdf2ca21d28b70f7656db3341c8ff5915","tid":1463784,"uid":127309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:49:27.000Z","msg":"721 811 pish"},{"pid":"31d53c784714622ff3885ac7fe998b47f2e049cd","tid":1463784,"uid":42242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:51:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 811<br />\n黑警死全家</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f0ac089977e7b551cf0b59e34aa341652234850e","tid":1463784,"uid":151507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:51:21.000Z","msg":"中銀無乜錢，不過都會買美金賣hkd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd484a928009576bc3ff21cc2608ec697c333bf","tid":1463784,"uid":279145,"like":0,"dislike":35,"score":-35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"樓主得一個post.  (自己諗） 完"},{"pid":"6f5c36686b7a6ccb05e12f434dc461e89bff1c35","tid":1463784,"uid":176279,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:02:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n政治問題經濟解決<br />\n我地永遠都揸住佢地春袋，所以我地先可以6月抗爭到而家<br />\n<br />\n「Use your leverage：了解自身的優勢，在談判中採取主動，把有限優勢無限擴大，善用槓桿，讓對方不得不跟你打交道」- the Art of Deal"},{"pid":"2ee564f0a7b3a6775f43032c749cf613dec546ae","tid":1463784,"uid":272119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:04:41.000Z","msg":"買午餐肉"},{"pid":"4a08a4e3de105a133394063ffca1b990e8cce9f2","tid":1463784,"uid":292881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a165f65001dcf4fae05b243b8b443d9c76ae0b0","tid":1463784,"uid":112094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97ce3c4a173b4e4ef75844cc45fa075cafe5aca","tid":1463784,"uid":91878,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"abd484a928009576bc3ff21cc2608ec697c333bf","tid":1463784,"uid":279145,"like":0,"dislike":35,"score":-35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"樓主得一個post.  (自己諗） 完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:07:43.000Z","msg":"起碼唔係P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a868fa401873dae7abd216d1268f46df536916df","tid":1463784,"uid":279145,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"e97ce3c4a173b4e4ef75844cc45fa075cafe5aca","tid":1463784,"uid":91878,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"abd484a928009576bc3ff21cc2608ec697c333bf","tid":1463784,"uid":279145,"like":0,"dislike":35,"score":-35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"樓主得一個post.  (自己諗） 完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:07:43.000Z","msg":"起碼唔係P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"你的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vokEzyc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvokEzyc.png&h=0eddf172&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a8b7c10b3bc7e25823f3ef34cff1ff060607332","tid":1463784,"uid":14144,"like":